title: Neon Russian Words Decal Pack
longDescription:
Russian Words Decal Pack

All of these drawings contain high quality, the colors of these drawings can be changed, you can even create designs as you want with simple parameter settings, if you want to change the main source file of these designs, if you send your invoice via discord we can share the "AI SOURCES" files with you...


What are AI SOURCES files?


  • With these source files, you can output 64x64 or 32k and above without losing quality, since these designs are vectoral, the quality never deteriorates.
  • With these source files, you can create as many original designs as you want.
